{"id": "vos006", "name": "???_???_144_??_??", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Shelter System]"], "content": "<i>Units: Constructor, Caretaker, please move to entrance A. Prepare to head to Node 08 to perform routine construction work.</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ivy... will be sent to another group today as well?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>Reminder, 2501 No.5, you have left the work formation. Please return to your work station.</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Ah, damn...</font>\nReceived.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>No. 5, your reaction speed often surpasses the standard reaction time. Do you need to go to the service district for a check-up? </i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "... No, there are no errors. Continuing to execute the mission.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>Received.</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Servo", "Working"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>No. 5, please take building materials from group C and D to Coordinates 22, 346.</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Understood.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "Footsteps."], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→File Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Hehe, thanks.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\nActually... there's something I haven't told you.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "What is it?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Ilka's plan... it doesn't just involve humans. She also plans on eradicating unawakened Architects, including those who can't break free from the protocol... those called the \"half-awakened\".\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "This is why I want you to keep your distance from her. I don't want to hide this from you. They want me to join. If I join them, I can definitely better avoid the system check-ups and won't be destroyed. For now, I haven't answered them, because they don't consider you to be fully awakened.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "I don't know what to do. But they do see me as an ally; as long as I'm around, they won't touch you.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Is it because... I have to synch with the matrix regularly?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Yes... That's a result of not being able to break free from the protocol. Ilka... perhaps something happened in her past which caused her to think that in the end, the half-awakened will be controlled by the protocol, even if they can think. She won't trust them.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "What if... starting from now, I don't synch with the matrix. Will she accept me then?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "... Huh? If you do that, your system...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Do you agree with what I just said, Ivy?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "... Yeah. Compared to conflict, your ideas are worth considering.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Well, everyone has the ability to think for themselves. IIka seems very intelligent; she'll understand.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "I... I can't promise you that. She's very resolute.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "Stands Up"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "In any case, there has to be a way. The Blessed... there's not that many. It'd be best for everyone to stick together.\n'Kay, about time to head back.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Hey, Vanessa. You better go back and synch. Don't think that because of all this...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Haha, relax. I'm going right now. I wouldn't make Ivy worry.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→File Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Is that......Vanessa? She looks distracted...</font>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "Stumbles"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Wah!?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Move_Obj_01", "Supplies Topple"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Vanessa! Be careful!</font>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Ah!!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "Sprints"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Impact_02", "Loud Noise"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "... What are you doing? Focus on your work. Do you want to be reprocessed?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "image", "attrs": ["vos0601"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......Ilka......!?\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>Error detected, report your condition.</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Eh... I...</font>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Error report; calculation inaccuracy caused a delay in movement.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>OPCI_2404_IL, report the time of your last synchronization.</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Scan", "Data Input"], "content": ""}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>... Normal. Please clear your work schedule and head to the service district for a status check-up.</i>\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "Understood.\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "Footsteps."], "content": ""}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka...\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "... You... how long has it been since your last synch?\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "... I...\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "If you want to live, then accept your fate. You cannot free yourself from the protocol. Due to Ivy's position, for the time being, I do not wish for anything to befall you. At least until the very end... Get up.\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "Footsteps."], "content": ""}, {"id": 62, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......\nUm... wait!\n"}, {"id": 63, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "I do not know... any way to awaken you. So long as you remain in your current condition, there is nothing I can do to help you... I'm sorry.\n"}, {"id": 64, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 65, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 66, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Ivy", "Hurried Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 67, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa! Are you alright!?\n"}, {"id": 68, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ivy... I'm fine. Didn't mean for you to see me embarass myself...\n"}, {"id": 69, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "What, what did she say to you?\n"}, {"id": 70, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "She said... she wants me to live, at least until \"the very end\"...\n"}, {"id": 71, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\nShe shouldn't have any reason to help you. Even though she wants to think of a way to pull me in... I don't know what she's thinking.\n"}, {"id": 72, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "I don't know either... but... she looked so... sad...\n"}, {"id": 73, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 74, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Switches]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Shelter システム]"], "content": "<i>ユニット：Constructor、Caretakerは、エントランスAまで移動して、Node08のルーチン建設の準備を行ってください。</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ivy……今日も別々なの？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>リマインド：2501ユニット5、フォーメーションから外れています。持ち場に戻ってください。</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">わ、大変……</font>\n了解。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>ユニット5、反応遅延を確認。\nメンテナンスエリアにてメンテナンスを行いますか？</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……いいえ。異常はありません。\n任務を継続します。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>了解。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Servo", "工事"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>ユニット5、CとDの建材を座標22,346まで運んでください。</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "了解。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→ファイル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "へへ、ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "………\nあなたに伝えないといけないことがもう一つある……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "なに？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Ilkaはこの計画で……人類だけじゃなくて、覚醒していないアーキテクトも、プロトコルから逃れられない「半覚醒者」も消そうとしてる。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……えっ！？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "だから、あなたには彼女に近寄らないでほしいって言った。\nでも、あなたに隠し事をするのはイヤだから……\nあいつらは、私を仲間に引き入れようとしてる。\n確かに仲間になればシステムのチェックに引っかかる確率も減ると思う。\n引っかからなければ排除されることもない。\nでも、まだ返事はしてない。\nだって、あなたのような特殊な状況のユニットを除外しようとしているから。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "どうすればいいのか、私にもまだわかってない。\nでも、あいつらは私のことを仲間だと思ってる。\n私がいる限り、あなたには手を出させないから。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "それは……私が定期的にメインフレームと同期しないといけないから？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "そう……それもあなたがプロトコルの制御を逃れられないことが原因。\nIlkaは……過去に何かあったのかもしれない。\nだから半覚醒者はたとえ自我があったとしても、最終的にプロトコルから逃れることは不可能で信頼できないって考えてるのかも。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "今からでも……私がメインフレームとの同期をやめたら……私のことを認めてくれるかな？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……何を言ってるの？\nそんなことしたらあなたは……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "さっき私が言ったこと……Ivyもわかってくれるよね？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……うん。\n無意味な衝突を生むより、あなたの考え方は参考になった。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "みんな思考能力を持ってる。\nIlkaは頭もよさそうだし、きっとわかってくれるはず。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "それは……わからない。\n自分の考えをそうやすやすと変えるようには見えない。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "起き上がる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "とにかく方法はあるはず。\n「祝福されし者」はそんなに多くないし……お互いに助け合って団結しないと。\nじゃあ、私そろそろ行くね。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "ねぇ、Vanessa。\n同期は必ずすること。\n絶対に……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "あはは！大丈夫。\n今からちゃんと行くよ。\nIvy、心配しないで。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→ファイル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">あれは……Vanessa？\nボーっとして……</font>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "つまづく"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "きゃっ！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Move_Obj_01", "建材が崩れる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Vanessa！危ない！</font>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">きゃあ！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Impact_02", "大きな音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……何をしている？\n仕事に集中するんだ。\n再構築されたいのか？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "image", "attrs": ["vos0601"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……Ilka……！？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>エラー発生。状況報告をしてください。</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">え……あ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "アクシデントレポート。\nオペレーションの誤差により動作に遅延が発生しています。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>OPCI_2404_IL、前回の同期時刻を報告してください。</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Scan", "データ転送"], "content": ""}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>……問題ありません。\nタスクをリセットしてメンテナンスエリアへ移動してください。</i>\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "了解。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka……\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……いつから……同期をしていない。\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……私……\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "生きたければ諦めろ。\nお前はプロトコルの制御から逃れられない。\nIvyのためにも、現時点でお前に何かあっては困る。\n少なくとも最後の時までは……ほら。\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 62, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "………\nあの……っ！待ってください！\n"}, {"id": 63, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "私はお前を覚醒者にする方法は知らない。\n現状を抜け出せない限り、私がお前のためにしてやれることもない……悪いな。\n"}, {"id": 64, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 65, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 66, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Ivy", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 67, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa！大丈夫！？\n"}, {"id": 68, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ivy……私は大丈夫。\n恥ずかしいところを見せちゃったね……\n"}, {"id": 69, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "なんて言われた？\n"}, {"id": 70, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "生きろって……少なくとも「最後の時」までは……\n"}, {"id": 71, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "………\n私を仲間に入れたいからといって、彼女がVanessaを助ける理由はない。\nいったいなにを考えて……\n"}, {"id": 72, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "私にもわからない……でも……すごく悲しい顔をしてた……\n"}, {"id": 73, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 74, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Shelter 系統]"], "content": "<i>單位：Constructor、Caretaker，請移至 A 入口，準備前往 Node 08 進行例行建設。</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ivy……今天也被分配到別組嗎？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>提醒，2501 五號機，您已脫離陣列，請回到工作崗位。</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">啊、糟糕……</font>\n收到。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>五號機，反應時長超過標準，是否需要前往維修區檢測？</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……不，沒有異常，繼續執行任務。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>收到。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Servo", "施工"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>五號機，請將 C 組、 D 組建材送往 22, 346 座標。</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "了解。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換檔案]</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "嘻嘻，謝謝妳。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n其實……還有一件事我沒告訴妳。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "什麼事？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Ilka 的計畫中……除了人類，也打算剷除所有未覺醒的建造者，包括無法脫離協定影響的機體……他們稱為「半覺醒者」。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……咦！？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "這就是我要妳遠離她的理由，我不想隱瞞妳。他們想拉我入夥，如果跟他們在一起，的確比較能規避系統的檢測，不會被銷毀。但我暫時沒有答應他們，因為他們將妳這樣特殊狀況的機體排除在外。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "我也還不知道現在該怎麼辦，不過他們將我視為同伴，只要我還在，他們應該不會對妳出手的。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "是因為……我定期要回母體同步嗎？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "嗯……那也是因為妳無法脫離協定造成的。Ilka 以前……也許經歷過什麼，才會覺得半覺醒者無論擁有什麼思維，到最終都會被協定控制，無法信任。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "如果我……從現在開始不回母體同步，她會認可我嗎？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……妳在說什麼？這麼做的話妳的系統……\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "我剛剛說的那些，Ivy 也能認同吧？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……嗯。的確比起衝突，妳的想法也很有參考價值。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "那麼，大家同樣都擁有自我思考的能力，Ilka 看起來很聰明，一定也能理解的。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "這……我就不敢保證了，她的態度很堅定。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "起身"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "總之，一定會有辦法的。「眷顧者」……數量已經那麼少了，大家應該互相團結才對。\n好了，我差不多該回去了。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "喂，Vanessa，一定要回去同步啊。不要因為這種事……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "哈哈，放心。我現在就正要去了，不會讓 Ivy 擔心的。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換檔案]</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">那是……Vanessa？看起來心不在焉的……</font>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "絆倒"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "哇！？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Move_Obj_01", "建材崩塌"], "content": ""}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Vanessa！危險！</font>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">呀！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Running_step_02", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Impact_02", "巨響"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……妳在幹嘛？專心工作，想被重製嗎？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "image", "attrs": ["vos0601"], "content": ""}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……Ilka……！？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>發現異常，回報狀況。</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">咦……我……</font>\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "問題回報，運算誤差導致動作計算延遲。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>OPCI_2404_IL，回報上次同步時間。</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Scan", "資料傳輸"], "content": ""}, {"id": 54, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>……正常。請清除工作列表，回檢修區檢查系統狀態。</i>\n"}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "是。\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ilka……\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "……妳……多久沒有回去同步了？\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……我……\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "還想活就認命吧，妳脫離不了協定的。因為 Ivy 的立場，我暫時不希望妳出事，至少到最後一刻……起來。\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 62, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……。\n那個……請等一下！\n"}, {"id": 63, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ilka"], "content": "我不知道……讓妳成為覺醒者的方法，但只要妳還是這個狀態，就沒有什麼我能為妳做的……抱歉。\n"}, {"id": 64, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 65, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 66, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Ivy", "急促腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 67, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Vanessa！沒事吧！？\n"}, {"id": 68, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ivy……我沒事。不好意思讓妳看到我出糗了……\n"}, {"id": 69, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "那傢伙，跟妳說了什麼？\n"}, {"id": 70, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "她說……要我好好活著，至少到「最後一刻」……\n"}, {"id": 71, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n她應該沒有理由幫妳的，就算再怎麼想拉我入夥也……不知道她在想什麼。\n"}, {"id": 72, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "我也不清楚……不過……她的表情，看起來好悲傷……\n"}, {"id": 73, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 74, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Shelter 시스템]"], "content": "<i>유닛: Constructor, Caretaker는 A입구로 이동 바람. Node 08의 건설 작업 준비를 시작하도록.</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "Ivy......오늘도 다른 그룹에 배치된 거야?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>알림, 2501 5호기 근무지 이탈, 즉시 본래 자리로 복귀하기 바람.</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">아, 이런......</font>\n알겠다.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>5호기, 응답 속도가 기준치에 미달했다. 점검소에서 검사를 진행할 필요가 있는 것인가?</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......아니, 아무 이상 없다. 임무를 지속하겠다.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>알겠다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Servo", "공사"], "content": ""}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCI_2103_I"], "content": "<i>5호기, C그룹, D그룹의 자재를 22. 346 좌표로 보내주기 바란다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "알겠다.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→파일 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "헤헤, 고마워\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......\n사실......한 가지 더 네게 말해줄 것이 있어.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "무슨 일인데?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "Ilka의 계획은... 인간뿐만이 아니라 각성을 이루지 못한 아키텍트 역시 제거 대상으로 삼고 있어. 협정의 영향으로부터 벗어나지 못한 모든 기체를 포함해서 말이야... 그들은 이들을 [반각성자]라고 부르고 있어.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......뭐! ? \n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "이것이 바로 녀석에게 가까이하지 말라고 했던 이유야. 네게 숨기고 싶은 마음은 없어. 그들은 나를 동료로 삼고 싶어 해. 만약 그들과 함께 있으면, 비교적 수월하게 시스템 점검을 피할 수 있을 거고 폐기되지도 않을 거야. 하지만 아직 그들에게 대답은 하지 않았어. 왜냐하면 너처럼 특수한 상황에 처해있는 기체는 제외해버렸거든.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "나도 지금 어떻게 해야할 지 모르겠어. 그래도 그들은 나를 동료로 생각하고 있으니까, 내가 있으면 아마 그들도 네게 무슨 짓을 하거나 그러진 않을 거야.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "그건... 내가 정기적으로 모체와 동기화를 해야하기 때문이야?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "응......그것도 네가 협정으로부터 벗어날 수 없기 때문이기도 하지. llka는 아마도... 예전에 어떤 일을 겪었고 그로 인해 반각성자들은 어떤 자의적인 사고도 해낼 수 없어서 결국 마지막엔 협정의 지배를 받게 될 것이라고... 신뢰해선 안된다는 생각을 갖게 된 것 같아.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "만약에... 지금부터라도 내가 모체와 동기화를 하지 않으면... 나를 인정해줄까?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......무슨 말이야? 그렇게 하면 네 시스템은...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "내가 조금 전에 말했던 것들... Ivy도 알아줄까?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "......응. 서로 충돌하는 것보다는 네 생각이 더 참고할만한 가치가 있다고 생각하니까.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "그럼, 모두가 자주적 사고 능력을 가지고 있다는 말을 분명 이해해주겠지? Ilka는 엄청 똑똑해 보이던데.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "그건... 나도 장담 못하겠어. 아주 견고한 태도를 취하고 있어서...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "몸을 일으킨다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "어쨌든, 분명 방법이 있을 거야. [권고자]들의 수가... 벌써 얼마 남지 않았어. 모두들 서로 힘을 모아야만 해. \n얘기 잘 들었어. 나는 이제 가봐야할 것 같아.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Ivy"], "content": "저기, Vanessa. 꼭 돌아가서 동기화하도록 해. 방금 말한 것 때문에 괜히...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "하하하! 안심해! 지금 막 하러 가려던 길이니까. Ivy가 걱정하지 않도록 말이야.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→파일 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vanessa"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type":